# Athens Tech Kit
**Outside Inn Studios | Mar–May 2026 | Living Document**

> Single reference for all hardware traveling to Athens. Optimized for Notion, GitHub, and AI project context. Update this file when anything changes.

---

## Carry-On Only — Cannot Be Checked

| Item | Why |
|---|---|
| AERO X16 Laptop | Theft + damage risk in hold |
| Anker 737 Power Bank (24,000mAh / 88.8Wh) | Lithium battery — banned from checked bags |
| TalentCell Mini UPS (97.2Wh) | Lithium battery — banned from checked bags |
| ELECOM NESTOUT Power Bank | Lithium battery — banned from checked bags |
| SanDisk 2TB Extreme SSD | All stream source files live here |
| Samsung T9 2TB SSD | Backup — irreplaceable data |
| iPad | Chat monitor |
| SanDisk 256GB microSD | GoPro card |

> ⚠️ TalentCell is 97.2Wh — just under the 100Wh carry-on limit. Label confirms. Fine without approval.

