## Streaming Stack

| Item | Role |
|---|---|
| GL.iNet GL-MT6000 Router | Primary router — apartment WAN in, laptop LAN out |
| AT&T Hotspot | 5G backup internet on WAN2 — needs Greek SIM (get at Athens airport) |
| TalentCell Mini UPS | Keeps router alive during power flickers |
| Anker 7-in-1 USB-C Hub | Primary streaming hub — PD charging + Yeti + spare USB-A |
| Insignia USB-C Hub | Backup hub — HDMI + 2× USB-A + USB-C |
| BENFEI USB-C to Ethernet Adapter | Backup ethernet path |
| Ethernet cables | Wired laptop → router — always wired when streaming |

